{
  "id": "RAW_5f5e94",
  "title": "我整理了 10+提示词，这才是 Qwen3 的正确打开姿势",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwMTU5OTQ1Nw==&mid=2653718812&idx=1&sn=f3f4f650a11b6630231c68c54ff06e7d&subscene=0",
  "date": "2025-05-03 09:27:00",
  "author": "冷逸",
  "siteName": "沃垠AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 40px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"506235139\" data-ratio=\"0.42592592592592593\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4f8a4f14-02ff-41c8-6cbe-60d79d25cf00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4f8a4f14-02ff-41c8-6cbe-60d79d25cf00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">4月29日，阿里发布并开源了新一代模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">Qwen3</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（简称千问3）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，带来了国内首款“</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">混合推理模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">”。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6648148148148149\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235140\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/69cd6f00-433e-4e76-e17c-12acc113ec00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/69cd6f00-433e-4e76-e17c-12acc113ec00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图用千问3生成</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前，阿里云百炼、通义、Qwen Chat均已支持使用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">通义：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">网页（tongyi.com）&amp;通义APP使用。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">阿里云百炼：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">网页对话+API调用，支持8个全尺寸模型。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">Qwen Chat：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">网页对话形式，支持235B-A22B、30B-A3B、32B三个尺寸。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">千问3上线后，很多人跑去问了几个问题，或者让它写了首诗，觉得似乎“不过尔尔”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那是因为你仍把它当AI Chat</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（聊天机器人）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">用，并未解锁千问3的最新技能</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">混合推理、更轻更快、MCP&amp;工具调用、数学&amp;代码增强、多语言支持</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">等）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">今天，我就给大家分享几个千问3的Prompt。部分</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">个人原创</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，部分引用自其他作者</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（有注明来源）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">看完，你也学会，一键上手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"506234803\" data-ratio=\"0.2828282828282828\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"396\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3d1aa662-7393-48d8-a3c2-0bd3601fe700/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3d1aa662-7393-48d8-a3c2-0bd3601fe700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(210, 79, 240);font-weight: bold;\">Show case</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">1）将文件转为可视化网页</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可视化，我们之前分享过一期文章，当时用的是DeepSeek-V3-0324模型。新一版Qwen3，代码能力显著增强，比之前的Qwen-2.5-Max和QwQ-32B都要强，接近Claude 3.5的水平。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这里，给大家分享上传文档生成可视化网页的prompt，擅长做财报、技术论文或公众号长文的总结。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">提示词一作来自</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">藏师傅</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，我做了细微修改。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"border:1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160);border-radius:5px;padding:10px;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;width:100%;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 14px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">将这个【xx文档】生成一个Html动态网页，要求：</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1.使用Bento Grid风格布局，纯x色底配合xx色作为高亮。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2.提炼文档内容，用超大字体或数字突出核心要点。画面中有超大视觉元素强调重点，与小元素文字形成反差。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3.运用高亮色自身透明度渐变制造科技感，但是不同高亮色不要互相渐变。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">4.数据可以引用在线的图表组件，样式需与主题一致。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">5.简洁的勾线图形化作为数据可视化或者配图元素。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">6.中英文混用，中文大字体粗体，英文小字作为点缀。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">7.模仿apple官网的动效，向下滚动鼠标配合动效。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">8.使用HTML5、TailwindCSS 3.0+(通过CDN引入)和必要的JavaScript。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">9.使用专业图标库如Font Awesome或Material Icons (通过CDN引入)。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">10.避免使用emoji作为主要图标。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">比如，我们拿比亚迪的2025Q1财报，让它生成一个财报解读网页。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/NX4HOlP6ibC8zpQiaico12xibKUViaqqNSmeD1EdxEfTRJHSFhXfM2ibmCMmom2icnA85Uib8EVCPznv13F1RYXXptBKRQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"935.2953736654805\" data-cropy2=\"574.9217081850534\" data-imgfileid=\"506235147\" data-ratio=\"0.613903743315508\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"935\" style=\"width: 558px;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/997e2ad3-a3f5-4bff-70e2-4428c4038200/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/997e2ad3-a3f5-4bff-70e2-4428c4038200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"border:1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160);border-radius:5px;padding:10px;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;width:100%;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 14px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">将这个【比亚迪2025年一季度财报】生成一个Html动态网页，要求：</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">1.使用Bento Grid风格布局，纯黑色底配合比亚迪红色#e70114作为高亮。</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">2.提炼文档内容，用超大字体或数字突出核心要点。画面中有超大视觉元素强调重点，与小元素文字形成反差。</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">3.运用高亮色自身透明度渐变制造科技感，但是不同高亮色不要互相渐变。</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">4.数据可以引用在线的图表组件，样式需与主题一致。</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">5.简洁的勾线图形化作为数据可视化或者配图元素。</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">6.中英文混用，中文大字体粗体，英文小字作为点缀。</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">7.模仿apple官网的动效，向下滚动鼠标配合动效。</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">8.使用HTML5、TailwindCSS 3.0+(通过CDN引入)和必要的JavaScript。</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">9.使用专业图标库如Font Awesome或Material Icons (通过CDN引入)。</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">10.避免使用emoji作为主要图标。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"506235141\" data-ratio=\"1.390607101947308\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"873\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9e1c03e5-35a0-4fc8-290a-4038cb052c00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9e1c03e5-35a0-4fc8-290a-4038cb052c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.3917525773195876\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"873\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235142\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/715e3e1c-49cc-4bb8-bdb0-c541188ffa00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/715e3e1c-49cc-4bb8-bdb0-c541188ffa00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">2）制作动画特效</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Qwen3不仅能写网页，还能制作一些动画特效，比如这个。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"border:1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160);border-radius:5px;padding:10px;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;width:100%;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 14px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">写一个漂亮的p5js粒子动画，随鼠标的移动而变化。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3969750893452394497\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3969750893452394497\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FNX4HOlP6ibC8zpQiaico12xibKUViaqqNSmeDN6fy9sZLr74O8FLmib0YFzn8XT026kqVmwRTgUI5aeU4gyHhlV8mYCQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我真的被惊艳到了。怎么实现的？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">先把上面的Prompt发给Qwen3，让它生成p5js代码。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8735868448098664\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"973\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235149\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250505081016_7fb855\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250505081016_7fb855\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然后，复制p5js代码，到预览网站</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">https://editor.p5js.org</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，运行代码，查看效果。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9046296296296297\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235148\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3026414c-7a22-4158-2cad-6095df1c4b00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3026414c-7a22-4158-2cad-6095df1c4b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">经典的旋转六边形case，Prompt来自X网友@_akhaliq。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"border:1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160);border-radius:5px;padding:10px;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;width:100%;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 14px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">写一个html应用程序，显示球在旋转的六边形内弹跳。球应该受到重力和摩擦力的影响，并且必须逼真地从旋转的墙壁上反弹。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.9141949152542372\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"944\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235151\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250505081016_2a3a98\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250505081016_2a3a98\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Qwen3是少见的能够正确处理受力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（重力和摩擦力）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">变化的模型，其他o3-mini、R1模型都不太行。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5505097312326228\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235152\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8b0fc65f-3516-4f14-8d37-d8bd47e78900/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8b0fc65f-3516-4f14-8d37-d8bd47e78900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">Qwen3的代码能力，真的被低估了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">3）制作路线规划网站</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Qwen3模型的一大亮点，是能支持MCP和工具调用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（function calling）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，比如地图、天气、搜索、图片生成、TTS音频合成、视频合成以及数据库管理等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前网页版还不支持MCP，我们可以在百炼上进行配置</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（送100万tokens）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，然后模型就可以进行调用了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">比如，我们让它调用高德地图，就可以制作一个路线规划网站。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"border:1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160);border-radius:5px;padding:10px;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;width:100%;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 14px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">我计划从成都开电车到武汉，我车的CLTC续航是600km，帮我创建一个网页，利用地图工具，来展示推荐的充电桩位置。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235154\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b6a435c-1712-456c-f1c1-59850425a200/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b6a435c-1712-456c-f1c1-59850425a200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">4）制作个人播客</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过配置的MCP，Qwen3也可以制作个人播客。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"border:1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160);border-radius:5px;padding:10px;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;width:100%;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 14px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">参考网易云音乐APP的播放界面，创建一个以我为中心的播客系统，播客音频围绕我的位置、个性爱好和本地资讯进行生成。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.6820388349514563\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"412\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235155\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0be3f5df-f7c6-440a-c320-3a27e50ad400/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0be3f5df-f7c6-440a-c320-3a27e50ad400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">5）制作天气卡片</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">原Prompt来自X网友@AGI_FromWalmart，我做了细微修改和汉化处理。如果我们接了天气API，数据会更加准确；如果没有，那就勾上联网功能。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"border:1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160);border-radius:5px;padding:10px;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;width:100%;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 14px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">联网搜索今日成都的天气，然后创建一个HTML文件，包含CSS和JavaScript，用于生成一个带动画效果的中文天气卡片。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">该卡片通过不同的动画，来直观展示天气情况：</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">风：例如移动的云朵、摇摆的树或风的动画；</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">雨：例如下落的雨滴、积水动画；</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">晴：例如耀眼的阳光、明亮背景动画；</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">雪：例如飘落的雪花、积雪动画。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">所有天气卡片并排显示。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">卡片背景为深色。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">将所有HTML、CSS和JavaScript代码写在同一个HTML文件中。JavaScript中应包含切换不同天气状态的方式（例如：一个函数或一组按钮），用于展示每种天气状态的动画效果。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.2450980392156863\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"510\" style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235156\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d53989f3-7272-4a6c-4959-027d9d216400/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d53989f3-7272-4a6c-4959-027d9d216400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">6）提示词命令no_think</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们知道，模型思考得越多，其解决问题的能力也就越强。但思考久了也有代价——耗时，浪费token。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6185185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235068\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c7ecec96-a2ed-498d-b8da-8cb93642f100/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c7ecec96-a2ed-498d-b8da-8cb93642f100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于简单问题，建议直接回答，不要思考。复杂问题，才需要开启思考。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Qwen3带来了国内首款“混合推理模型”，我们可以手动选择或口令选择是否需要开启think模式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">比如下图，即使我已经勾选了“深度思考”，但依然还是能通过口令“请不要思考”，让模型立即切换到no_think模式，快速回答。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7527777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235157\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ce4f971d-00a8-4dbe-a77d-e273d95cfd00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ce4f971d-00a8-4dbe-a77d-e273d95cfd00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同时，Qwen Chat还支持调整思考的长度，最长支持38912 tokens的思考，调整至0就是关闭思考的意思。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.46266471449487556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"683\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235158\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/98ebde06-c04c-49e5-fc57-b8b548008d00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/98ebde06-c04c-49e5-fc57-b8b548008d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">7）制作学习计划</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"border:1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160);border-radius:5px;padding:10px;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;width:100%;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 14px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">你是一名计算机专业教授，我是人工智能专业的大二学生，正在攻克自然语言处理课程，帮我制作一个为期20天的学习计划。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">有2点要注意：</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1）周末我要休息，无法学习。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2）学习内容除了课本和章节外，还要给我一些练习题。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8735868448098664\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"973\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235159\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250505081016_5b739f\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250505081016_5b739f\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">8）编写多语言邮件</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"border:1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160);border-radius:5px;padding:10px;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;width:100%;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 14px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">将这封给客户的英文道歉邮件改写成礼貌的日本商务风格（敬语），保留温暖但添加适当的敬语。</span></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;My Sincere Apologies</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Dear [Recipient's Name],</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">I hope this email finds you well. I am writing to sincerely apologize for [describe the issue briefly, e.g., \"the delay in submitting the report,\" \"missing our meeting yesterday,\" or \"the misunderstanding during our conversation\"].</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">I understand that this has caused [mention the impact, e.g., \"inconvenience to you,\" \"disruption to the project,\" or \"frustration on your part\"], and I take full responsibility for my actions. This was entirely my fault, and I deeply regret any trouble it may have caused.</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">To make it right, [explain how you plan to fix the issue, e.g., \"I have already submitted the report and will ensure it doesn’t happen again,\" \"I’d like to reschedule the meeting at your earliest convenience,\" or \"I will clarify the details with the team immediately\"].</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Once again, I am truly sorry for the situation, and I appreciate your understanding and patience. Please let me know if there’s anything else I can do to rectify this.</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Best regards,</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">[Your Full Name]</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">[Your Position/Role]</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">[Your Contact Information, if needed]</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6002034587995931\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"983\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506235160\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4bde2b00-1d3f-49c8-6e1c-7901ca517c00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4bde2b00-1d3f-49c8-6e1c-7901ca517c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2828282828282828\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"396\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506234801\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e0505f39-7dbb-442e-9482-fa34fea94d00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e0505f39-7dbb-442e-9482-fa34fea94d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(210, 79, 240);font-weight: bold;\">写在最后</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">都说，模型即产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但产品也需要场景，需要应用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">于是，我提了一个暴论：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">提示词即应用，提示词即场景。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6853448275862069\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"696\" style=\"width: 558px;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 6px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/NX4HOlP6ibC8zpQiaico12xibKUViaqqNSmeDLamck5Edkc9aibzt1jheNYMB5Sktc1qS2XqHKBUK502g51KVkVm7eIA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"696.0106761565836\" data-cropy2=\"476.48042704626334\" data-imgfileid=\"506235162\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a9e2ed49-fdd1-4ed9-25a1-91331991fc00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a9e2ed49-fdd1-4ed9-25a1-91331991fc00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">无论何时，Prompt都不会过时，反而随着模型的进步而越发重要。只不过，过去我们写Prompt是人写，而现在是我们设计框架，AI帮写，人再来改。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从纯人工，走到了人机协作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Prompt，它就像创意一样，是我们能否驾驭技术的关键钥匙。好的模型，得配上好的Prompt，这样才能发挥它100%的功效。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最近半年里，大家都在说，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">我们缺一款国产Claude</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。Qwen3，不只是国产版Claude，还是Llama版Claude。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">又或许，它谁也不是，它就是千问3。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那个从一点一滴中进化，从一步一款个中迭代出来的Qwen</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（kūn）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">经历两年多…的练习<img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"128\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 20px;vertical-align: middle;background-size: cover;height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://res.wx.qq.com/t/wx_fed/we-emoji/res/assets/newemoji/Yellowdog.png\" src=\"https://res.wx.qq.com/t/wx_fed/we-emoji/res/assets/newemoji/Yellowdog.png\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现已成为全球开源的王。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这，就是千问。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "介绍了阿里 Qwen3 大语言模型的混合推理等创新功能，并分享了 10 多个实用提示词案例",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "介绍了阿里 Qwen3 大语言模型的混合推理等创新功能，并分享了 10 多个实用提示词案例",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了阿里最新发布的 Qwen3 大语言模型的功能特性，包括国内首创的混合推理模式（可灵活切换思考深度）、工具调用等新能力。作者通过 10 多个具体案例展示了 Qwen3 在实际应用中的表现，包括文档可视化网页生成、动画特效制作、路线规划网站开发、个人播客创建、多语言邮件改写等场景。特别介绍了 no_think 模式在提升响应效率方面的优势。每个案例都提供了详细的提示词模板和使用方法，具有很强的实践指导价值。文章最后强调了提示词工程在 AI 应用中的重要性，并对 Qwen3 的发展前景进行了展望。",
